high_descs: Turn around and face the white table.
Take the knife under the lettuce from the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Move to the right slightly while facing the table.
Put the knife on the gray plate.
Move to the left slightly while facing the table.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Move to the right slightly while facing the table.
Put the lettuce on the gray plate.
Take the gray plate from the table.
Go to the left to the black stand to the left of the white table.
Put the plate on the right side of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a gray plate with a slice of lettuce on it on a stand.

high_descs: Turn around and face the white table
Grab the silver knife off of the table
Cut the cabbage into slices
Turn slightly to the right
Place the knife on the platter on the table
Turn slightly to the left
Grab one of the slices of cabbage
Turn slightly to the right
Place the cabbage on the platter
Grab the platter with the knife and cabbage on it
Turn left and stop at the black table
Place the platter on the black table
anns.task_desc: Moving a platter to the black table

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter with the lettuce on it.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Slice the lettuce on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the square bowl on the counter on your left.
Place the knife in the square bowl in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter with the lettuce on your right.
Take a lettuce slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the square bowl on the counter on your left.
Place the lettuce slice on the square bowl on the counter in front of you.
Pick up the square bowl with the lettuce and knife in front of you on the counter.
Turn left and face the square black table on your right.
Place the square bowl with lettuce on the black table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a lettuce slice on a plate on a black table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the table.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Step to the right and face the plate on the table.
Put the knife down on the plate on the table.
Step to the left and face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Step to the right and face the plate on the table.
Put the slice of lettuce on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the knife and lettuce on it.
Step to the left to face the black table beside the white table.
Place the plate with knife and lettuce on it on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of lettuce, place the lettuce plus the knife on a plate, move plate from white table to the black table.

high_descs: Turn around walk straight and face the left side of the white table
Pick up the butter knife from the table
Slice the lettuce head with the knife
Turn to the right then back to the left and face the middle of the white table
Place the knife on the silver plate
Turn to the left then slightly walk forward and turn right and face the left side of the white table
Pick up a slice from the lettuce head
Turn to the right then back to the left and face the middle of the white table
Place the piece of lettuce on the silver plate with the knife
Pick up the silver plate with the lettuce and knife on it
Turn to the left and walk slightly forward and face the small black shelf on the right
Place the silver plate with the lettuce and knife on the top black shelf
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce head and place it on a plate
